Class Http2Negotiator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.transport.netty.Http2Negotiator

  • public class Http2Negotiator
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class that provides support methods for negotiating the use of HTTP/2 with the remote endpoint.
